WEBVTT

00:00:00.602 --> 00:00:04.780
-se azoy a gedakht vos zey viln lozn far di kinder, far di eyniklekh, a may-

00:00:04.780 --> 00:00:06.332
epes

00:00:06.332 --> 00:00:08.372
zey zoln dos mit- mitnemen.

00:00:06.677 --> 00:00:07.633
ya.

00:00:08.213 --> 00:00:11.464
yo. ikh hob gevolt zogn

00:00:11.470 --> 00:00:14.906
az ikh bin zeyer shtolts

00:00:15.148 --> 00:00:17.217
fun mayne ale kinder

00:00:17.224 --> 00:00:21.633
un fun mayne k- eyniklekh un mayne ureyniklekh

00:00:21.633 --> 00:00:27.286
vayl ikh ze az on tsu gloybn, on tsu farshteyn vi azoy

00:00:27.286 --> 00:00:31.477
kh'hob bakumen fun di eybershter a gvaldike matone

00:00:31.737 --> 00:00:33.623
a matone vos

00:00:33.623 --> 00:00:36.854
ikh muz dos onerkenen

00:00:36.854 --> 00:00:38.357
in yede tog.

00:00:38.357 --> 00:00:40.078
s'iz nishto a moment

00:00:40.078 --> 00:00:43.779
vos ikh zol nisht zogn "HODU LASHEM."

00:00:44.022 --> 00:00:46.693
az kh'hob gegat a groyse

00:00:46.693 --> 00:00:47.728
mazl

00:00:47.768 --> 00:00:50.541
tsu hobn, un tsu hobn lebn mir

00:00:50.541 --> 00:00:53.820
un hinter mir aza sheyne

00:00:53.927 --> 00:00:56.236
doyre vos

00:00:56.236 --> 00:00:59.079
vos zenen ale Belzer khsidim

00:00:59.079 --> 00:01:01.701
un vos me farshteyt zikh azoy gut

00:01:01.909 --> 00:01:07.905
un ven ikh kum bay mayn eynikl vos der man, er iz a ekhte Belzer khosid

00:01:07.905 --> 00:01:14.089
un vos er lernt di gantse tsayt, iz zeyer ernst in ales vos er tut

00:01:14.089 --> 00:01:17.658
un er, er zet mir onkumen mit aza freyd

00:01:17.658 --> 00:01:19.468
vayl ikh makh tsu esn

00:01:19.468 --> 00:01:24.518
un er veyst az bay nakht vet er hobn a gute moltsayt.

00:01:24.535 --> 00:01:26.248
s'iz nisht keyn khilek.

00:01:26.248 --> 00:01:29.779
dos iz mayn kleyne PARTICIPATION

00:01:29.779 --> 00:01:31.449
vos ikh ken gebn

00:01:31.449 --> 00:01:33.299
far di, far di kinder

00:01:33.299 --> 00:01:35.799
un ikh for mit di AUTOBUS mit aza

00:01:35.799 --> 00:01:36.649
freyd

00:01:36.649 --> 00:01:41.070
un ikh shlof mikh ayn, un ikh vek mikh oyf, un ahin un aher.

00:01:41.070 --> 00:01:42.590
kh'bin a bisele mid

00:01:42.590 --> 00:01:45.640
⟨teylsmol⟩ mit ales, ober ikh farges ales.

00:01:45.640 --> 00:01:47.570
ven ikh kum bay di kinder

00:01:47.570 --> 00:01:49.610
iz es a gvaldike freyd.

00:01:49.610 --> 00:01:52.400
un s'iz ale, s'iz nisht keyn khilek az dos iz

00:01:52.400 --> 00:01:54.790
di tekhter fun mayn tokhter.

00:01:54.790 --> 00:01:57.470
un az s'iz di kinder fun mayne zinen

00:01:57.470 --> 00:01:59.760
zenen far mir zeyer

00:01:59.760 --> 00:02:01.680
noent un zeyer

00:02:01.680 --> 00:02:05.980
 kh'hob zey zeyer, ikh hob zey ale lib, eyns un eyns

00:02:05.980 --> 00:02:09.040
vayl zenen ale sheyn un zis, un me redt yidish

00:02:09.136 --> 00:02:11.355
un m'hot aza gute KESHER

00:02:11.355 --> 00:02:13.683
vayl ikh trakht az di

00:02:13.683 --> 00:02:17.059
tsu zayn mit di yugnt, dos makht yung.

00:02:17.059 --> 00:02:20.096
dos git a yunge gedank

00:02:20.096 --> 00:02:23.865
un ikh hob geduld. ikh ken oyshern

00:02:23.865 --> 00:02:26.625
un ikh vil oyshern ale SIPURIM

00:02:26.625 --> 00:02:28.505
ales vos me dertseylt

00:02:28.505 --> 00:02:32.015
ikh bin greyt, un mayn greste

00:02:32.055 --> 00:02:33.613
vos ikh ken zogn

00:02:33.613 --> 00:02:34.828
az s'iz

00:02:34.828 --> 00:02:37.854
dos vos ikh hob bakumen iz es fun mayn mame

00:02:38.333 --> 00:02:42.242
vayl mayn mame iz gevezn a groyse PERSONALITE

00:02:42.417 --> 00:02:48.758
psikhologish, un zi hot undz gegebn far ale kinder, mayne brider un shvester

00:02:48.758 --> 00:02:50.386
a gvaldike

00:02:50.386 --> 00:02:53.632
zikherkeyt un a EQUILIBRE

00:02:53.638 --> 00:02:58.593
a glaykhgevikht vos me ken zikh gebn an eytse in ale

00:02:58.617 --> 00:03:00.315
meglekhkeytn

00:03:00.726 --> 00:03:03.594
un ikh bin zi zeyer dankbar

00:03:03.594 --> 00:03:05.514
un zi hot geflegt tsu zogn

00:03:05.514 --> 00:03:07.994
"a kleyne Khane Sorele fun Drilzh

00:03:07.994 --> 00:03:10.784
fun a dos, kuk vos ikh hob oyfgeshtelt.

00:03:10.784 --> 00:03:14.490
kuk di kinder." zi hot gekent di ⟨ureyniklekh⟩

00:03:14.597 --> 00:03:16.577
⟨vos⟩ zenen gevezn bay mir

00:03:16.577 --> 00:03:19.817
un zi hot azoy lib gegat, avade

00:03:19.817 --> 00:03:22.517
di, di meydelekh

00:03:22.517 --> 00:03:26.170
un zi hot mir gezogt "loz zey nisht avek, loz zey nisht avek.

00:03:26.170 --> 00:03:29.520
BERTHEle, derbarem dikh. vos vet men tun on Tsipoyrele?"

00:03:29.520 --> 00:03:32.276
ikh hob gezogt "mame, s'iz nisht mayns.

00:03:32.299 --> 00:03:34.371
s'iz fun YETI.

00:03:34.371 --> 00:03:39.661
zi hot mir geborgt eyn yor far di seminar, ober nisht mer. dos iz es.

00:03:39.792 --> 00:03:42.219
un di KESHER

00:03:42.219 --> 00:03:43.549
mit di

00:03:43.656 --> 00:03:45.991
ureynikl fun mayn mame

00:03:45.991 --> 00:03:48.431
biz mit ir, vayl zi iz shoyn gevezn groys

00:03:48.431 --> 00:03:49.981
iz gevezn oysnam

00:03:49.981 --> 00:03:51.831
vayl mayn mame hot gelebt bay mir

00:03:51.831 --> 00:03:53.351
tsvey un a halb yor.

00:03:53.351 --> 00:03:56.562
ven zi hot zikh nisht azoy gut gefilt, un s'iz gevezn

00:03:56.562 --> 00:03:58.730
METAPELET, mit dos, mit yents

00:03:58.730 --> 00:04:01.350
ober di kleyne iz gekumen fun di shule

00:04:01.350 --> 00:04:02.290
"MIMI"

00:04:02.290 --> 00:04:05.320
azoy hot men zi gerufn. "du veyst vos iz gevezn?"

00:04:05.320 --> 00:04:09.860
un zi hot dertseylt "ikh bin geganen shvimen, ikh bin geganen do un do un dort."

00:04:09.860 --> 00:04:13.496
un zi hot oyfgemakht di oygn. es iz ge- un ikh bin dankbar

00:04:13.496 --> 00:04:17.400
far yeder eyner vos iz gevezn do un vos hot geholfn

00:04:17.400 --> 00:04:20.100
undz tsu gebn a bisl freyd far mayn mame

00:04:20.100 --> 00:04:23.630
un ikh hof az m- ikh vel oykhet, un ikh hob shoyn

00:04:23.630 --> 00:04:25.640
BARUCH HASHEM di freyd

00:04:25.640 --> 00:04:27.018
un

00:04:27.193 --> 00:04:29.797
dos iz es. ikh meyn az s'iz

00:04:29.797 --> 00:04:33.307
ales vos ikh ken zogn. a groyse TODA

00:04:33.307 --> 00:04:34.376
LASHEM.

00:04:35.040 --> 00:04:36.958
ZEHU.

00:04:38.601 --> 00:04:42.749
dos iz a alte bild vos me hot getrofn bay di mame

00:04:42.749 --> 00:04:44.284
ven zi iz avek

00:04:44.284 --> 00:04:45.964
un dos bin ikh

00:04:45.964 --> 00:04:49.634
ven ikh hob gegat umgefer fir yor

00:04:49.634 --> 00:04:53.144
mit a BEN DOD vos hot geheysn Shmuel.

00:04:53.144 --> 00:04:55.675
kh'ken ni- ikh veyst nisht genoy vi azoy

00:04:55.675 --> 00:04:57.877
ober azoy hot mir gezogt di mame.

00:04:57.877 --> 00:05:00.527
dos, "du bist gevezn do mit Shmuel."

00:05:00.538 --> 00:05:01.949
dos iz es.

00:05:03.407 --> 00:05:06.019
dos iz a bild vos m'hot gemakht

00:05:06.019 --> 00:05:08.644
ven m'iz tsurikgekumen fun LYON

00:05:08.644 --> 00:05:09.982
mokh di krig

00:05:10.005 --> 00:05:14.693
un vos m'hot undz gegat gefregt "efsher vet men forn keyn Amerike."

00:05:14.693 --> 00:05:18.777
di bruder fun di mame hot undz gezogt az me ken

00:05:18.777 --> 00:05:22.059
efsher forn, ober bay sof s'hot zikh nisht gemakht.

00:05:22.059 --> 00:05:26.059
iz, oyf links iz mayn kleyne bruder BERNARD.

00:05:26.059 --> 00:05:28.286
di hoykhe iz JOJO.

00:05:28.286 --> 00:05:33.034
dos bin ikh untn. di mame, LUCIENNE, un di PAPA.

00:05:35.267 --> 00:05:39.440
yo, do bin ikh far tsu forn keyn Erets Yisroel

00:05:39.440 --> 00:05:40.943
als a meydl

00:05:40.943 --> 00:05:43.633
mit di shvartse rok un mit di breyte KOVA

00:05:43.633 --> 00:05:44.943
mit mayn CHAVERA

00:05:44.943 --> 00:05:46.103
CLAIRETTE

00:05:46.103 --> 00:05:49.013
vos iz gevezn oykhet a shokhnte fun undz

00:05:49.037 --> 00:05:50.381
in Pariz.

00:05:53.408 --> 00:05:56.434
dos iz a bild fun mayn khasene

00:05:56.434 --> 00:05:57.969
vos leyder

00:05:57.969 --> 00:06:00.720
fun di ale mentshn arum un arum

00:06:00.720 --> 00:06:02.092
iz nor do

00:06:02.115 --> 00:06:04.404
dray mentshn.

00:06:04.444 --> 00:06:09.731
 untn iz mayn kleyne shvester. oybn iz Rokhl, mayn NICHTE.

00:06:09.731 --> 00:06:12.127
oybn iz Leybish, di bruder

00:06:12.127 --> 00:06:13.950
fun mayn man.

00:06:13.950 --> 00:06:17.679
derlebn iz di mume Dvoyre.

00:06:17.679 --> 00:06:22.699
do, shpeter iz mayn mame. dernokhn a shvester, Ester

00:06:22.699 --> 00:06:26.611
fun mayn man, un ir man, Abe.

00:06:26.652 --> 00:06:29.245
untn iz do RACHEL

00:06:29.267 --> 00:06:30.943
khosn kale

00:06:30.943 --> 00:06:34.637
un di tate un mit ELAINE, oykhet a NICHTE.

00:06:34.637 --> 00:06:37.437
untn iz mayn kleyne shvester RONI.

00:06:40.152 --> 00:06:44.375
dos iz a bild vu m'iz gevezn in KNOKKE oyf CHOFESH

00:06:44.375 --> 00:06:46.147
iz

00:06:46.147 --> 00:06:49.207
di tate mit di mame, un mit di

00:06:49.281 --> 00:06:51.401
YETI un EMMANUEL.

00:06:53.770 --> 00:06:57.083
dos iz ikh mit mayn man

00:06:57.083 --> 00:07:00.935
di tsveyte ziveg vos m'iz gevezn oyf a khasene.

00:07:03.557 --> 00:07:06.580
dos iz a bild vos m'hot gemakht in Pariz

00:07:06.580 --> 00:07:10.190
oyf di bar mitsve fun an eynikl fun mayn shvester

00:07:10.190 --> 00:07:12.840
un mayn bruder iz gekumen fun Amerike.

00:07:12.840 --> 00:07:14.880
ikh bin gekumen fun Yisroel

00:07:14.880 --> 00:07:18.170
un mayn yingere shvester iz gekumen fun MARSEILLE

00:07:18.170 --> 00:07:20.650
un m'hot zikh ale tsuzamengenumen

00:07:20.650 --> 00:07:24.436
un m'hot zikh genumen a bild, vayl me hot gezogt "s'iz nisht ale mol

00:07:24.436 --> 00:07:27.026
vos ale ZAGDANSKIS zenen tsuzamen."

00:07:27.026 --> 00:07:30.023
un dort fun hintn iz do di bar mitsve bokher

00:07:30.023 --> 00:07:31.074
DAVID.

00:07:36.480 --> 00:07:41.371
do iz di bild fun di letste khasene vos m'hot gegat.

00:07:41.371 --> 00:07:43.982
dos iz fun mayn eynikl EZRIEL

00:07:43.982 --> 00:07:49.212
mit di froy, un dos links iz do ale froyen, di tekhter mit di eyniklekh.

00:07:49.212 --> 00:07:51.942
untn iz do ale kinderlekh, keyneynehore

00:07:51.942 --> 00:07:55.630
un UNK rekhts iz do ale mener mit di ale kinder

00:07:55.630 --> 00:07:57.090
un eyniklekh.
